Notes on scope:

The MIT license above covers the source code in this repository (everything
under `indexing/` and `src/`, plus the configuration and documentation
files). It does NOT extend to:

- The benchmark dataset under `data/raw/` (`documents_subset.parquet`,
  `questions_test.parquet`, `subset_manifest.json`). This is a subset of
  the EnterpriseRAG-Bench by Onyx, published under the MIT license:
    Dataset: https://huggingface.co/datasets/onyx-dot-app/EnterpriseRAG-Bench
    Code:    https://github.com/onyx-dot-app/EnterpriseRAG-Bench
    Paper:   https://arxiv.org/abs/2605.05253
- The third-party models (`nomic-embed-text`, Qwen 3.5 9B) — each carries
  its own upstream license (Apache-2.0 for both, served via Ollama).
- The npm dependencies (`@mariozechner/pi-agent-core`, `@mariozechner/pi-tui`,
  `@mariozechner/pi-ai`, `better-sqlite3`) — each carries its own license
  (all MIT at the time of writing).
